network.param.modules.receipts

Interface IOrder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBean
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Order

    public interface IOrder
extends IBean
    An interface represents the Order information.

    This interface IOrder will represents order discount, order date, order items. IOrder defines below categories of operations:

    • setDate method to set order date.

    • setDiscount method to set order discount.

    • getDiscount method for get order discount.

    • addOrderItem method to add order item.

    • addOrderItems method to add the order items.

    • setOrderItems method to set order items.

    • getOrderItems method for get order items.

    • getDate method for get the order date.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, Muthu ParamNetwork
